Package com.ibm.di.plugin.proxy

Provides classes for managing the common Java Proxy used by all plug-ins.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Proxy
    This is the common Java Proxy that is responsible for reading the appropriate configuration file and listening for incoming connections.
    ProxyCommandReceiver
    This class is responsible for handling each client's request.
    StopProxy
    This class represents a utility that connects to a running Java Proxy and sends a stop request.
